🐛 Fix broken nav, calculator, search results, thumbnails, help HTML 🐛

Navigation (critical):
- public/header.tmpl only had brand+icon, no hamburger/nav/search
- public/nav.tmpl had hamburger but .nav was display:none in CSS
- Mobile users could not navigate at all
- Fix: merge combined header (brand+search+actions+hamburger+panel)
  into public/header.tmpl, make public/nav.tmpl a placeholder

Calculator (math.go rewrite):
- Old code replaced ^ with ** (not valid Go syntax), breaking ALL
  expressions that went through parser.ParseExpr after preprocessing
- Old preprocess() replaced constant "e" via regex in raw strings
- Fix: let Go parser handle ^ as token.XOR, reinterpret as math.Pow
  in evalNode; handle constants via ast.Ident, not string replacement
- Add: sqrt, sin, cos, tan, asin, acos, atan, log, log2, ln, exp,
  cbrt, abs, ceil, floor, round functions
- Add: pi, e, tau, phi constants
- Pre-compile regexes instead of compiling on every call

Search results (search.tmpl + public.css):
- Description summary was truncated to 4 lines on all screens;
  removed line-clamp so full snippets display
- Max-width 800px too narrow for results; increase to 960px
- Image/video thumbnails broken when URL 404s or is empty: only
  showed placeholder when .Thumbnail field was empty, not when img
  src failed to load
- Fix: wrap image thumbs in .image-thumb-wrap with CSS ::before
  fallback emoji; video-thumbnail-container gets ::before fallback;
  thumbnail img sits above with z-index so fallback shows through
  when img fails
- Video play overlay and duration badge now have z-index:2 to layer
  above the thumbnail img (z-index:1) and fallback (z-index:0)
- Image grid: increase mobile height 120px→140px, tablet 140px→160px,
  desktop 160px→180px
- Video description: increase line-clamp from 2 to 3

Help page (help.tmpl):
- <section id="search-operators"> never closed before
  <section id="keyboard-shortcuts"> started — broken nested HTML
- Fix: add missing </section> closing tag

Contact form (pages.go):
- Captcha generated A+B values but handleContactSubmit never validated
- Fix: HMAC-signed captcha IDs (signCaptcha/verifyCaptcha) using
  server startTime as key, validated on submission
- Switch fmt.Printf to log.Printf for contact logging

Search results template:
- {{if .PublishedAt}} caused nil pointer on zero time.Time values
- Fix: {{if not (.PublishedAt.IsZero)}}

CSS (public.css):
- Add missing: .btn-danger, .contact-success, .form-error,
  .captcha-group, .form-actions, .last-updated styles
- Add favicon fallback CSS for broken favicon images
